# Thumbs Up Project Plan

[thumbs_up/docs/PLAN.md](../../thumbs_up/docs/PLAN.md) is the single source of
truth for this app's scope, remaining work, and progress log.

- At the start of work on the Thumbs Up app, check that file's
  **Status / todo checklist** and **Progress log** sections to see what's
  already done and what's still pending before planning new work.
- After completing meaningful work on the app, append a new dated entry to
  the **Progress log** section (don't rewrite prior entries) and update the
  checkbox states in **Status / todo checklist** so the doc stays accurate
  for the next session.
- Treat the rest of the doc (specs, tokens, roadmap) as stable reference
  material — only edit it if the plan itself actually changes.
